#: ../../library/locale.rst:688
msgid ""
"Extension modules should never call :func:`setlocale`, except to find out "
"what the current locale is.  But since the return value can only be used "
"portably to restore it, that is not very useful (except perhaps to find out "
"whether or not the locale is ``C``)."
msgstr ""
"MĂłdulos de extensĂŁo nunca devem chamar :func:`setlocale`, exceto para "
"descobrir qual ĂŠ a localidade atual. Mas uma vez que o valor de retorno sĂł "
"pode ser usado portavelmente para restaurĂĄ-lo, isso nĂŁo ĂŠ muito Ăştil (exceto "
"talvez para descobrir se a localidade ĂŠ ou nĂŁo ``C``)."

#: ../../library/locale.rst:693
msgid ""
"When Python code uses the :mod:`!locale` module to change the locale, this "
"also affects the embedding application.  If the embedding application "
"doesn't want this to happen, it should remove the :mod:`!_locale` extension "
"module (which does all the work) from the table of built-in modules in the :"
"file:`config.c` file, and make sure that the :mod:`!_locale` module is not "
"accessible as a shared library."
msgstr ""

#: ../../library/locale.rst:704
msgid "Access to message catalogs"
msgstr "Acesso a catĂĄlogos de mensagens"

#: ../../library/locale.rst:713
msgid ""
"The locale module exposes the C library's gettext interface on systems that "
"provide this interface.  It consists of the functions :func:`gettext`, :func:"
"`dgettext`, :func:`dcgettext`, :func:`textdomain`, :func:`bindtextdomain`, "
"and :func:`bind_textdomain_codeset`.  These are similar to the same "
"functions in the :mod:`gettext` module, but use the C library's binary "
"format for message catalogs, and the C library's search algorithms for "
"locating message catalogs."
msgstr ""
"O mĂłdulo locale expĂľe a interface gettext da biblioteca C em sistemas que "
"fornecem essa interface. Consiste nas funĂ§Ăľes :func:`gettext`, :func:"
"`dgettext`, :func:`dcgettext`, :func:`textdomain`, :func:`bindtextdomain` e :"
"func:`bind_textdomain_codeset`. Elas sĂŁo semelhantes Ă s mesmas funĂ§Ăľes no "
"mĂłdulo :mod:`gettext`, mas usam o formato binĂĄrio da biblioteca C para "
"catĂĄlogos de mensagens e os algoritmos de pesquisa da biblioteca C para "
"localizar catĂĄlogos de mensagens."

#: ../../library/locale.rst:720
msgid ""
"Python applications should normally find no need to invoke these functions, "
"and should use :mod:`gettext` instead.  A known exception to this rule are "
"applications that link with additional C libraries which internally invoke C "
"functions ``gettext`` or ``dcgettext``.  For these applications, it may be "
"necessary to bind the text domain, so that the libraries can properly locate "
"their message catalogs."
msgstr ""
"As aplicaĂ§Ăľes Python normalmente nĂŁo precisam invocar essas funĂ§Ăľes e devem "
"usar :mod:`gettext` em seu lugar. Uma exceĂ§ĂŁo conhecida a esta regra sĂŁo os "
"aplicativos que se vinculam a bibliotecas C adicionais que invocam "
"internamente ``gettext`` ou ``dcgettext``. Para essas aplicaĂ§Ăľes, pode ser "
"necessĂĄrio vincular o domĂ­nio de texto, para que as bibliotecas possam "
"localizar adequadamente seus catĂĄlogos de mensagens."

